:萊庫提斯在希臘的醫學外科學大會中展示他使用抗生素治療消化性潰瘍的成果，但不為主流醫學機構所接受。<ref name="RP-hp" />

;1966
:萊庫提斯的論文稿件遭《[[美國醫學會雜誌|美國醫學會雜誌》]]拒絕。<ref name="RP-hp" />

;1967
:{{le|伊東進|Susumu Ito}}觀察到類似曲狀桿菌的生物體黏附在胃的[[上皮組織|上皮]]。<ref>{{cite book |last=Ito |first=Susumu | editor=Heidel, US |editor2=Code, CF | title=Handbook of Physiology Section 6 Volume 2 | year= 1967 |publisher= American Physiological Society| pages= 705–741 | chapter= Anatomic structure of the gastric mucosa}}</ref>

;1968
:萊庫提斯因為用他的方法（包括使用抗生素）治療消化性潰瘍而遭罰4000[[德拉克馬|德拉克馬]]。<ref name="RP-hp" />

==1970–現在==
;1971
:霍華德·斯特恩（Howard Steer）從潰瘍病人的生物檢體中觀察到幽門螺桿菌。<ref name="HWS-hp">{{cite book |author=Steer, Howard W |chapter=The discovery of ''Helicobacter pylori'' in England in the 1970s |editor=Barry J. Marshall |title=Helicobacter pioneers: firsthand accounts from the scientists who discovered helicobacters, 1892–1982 |publisher=Blackwell |location=Oxford |year=2002 |pages=119–29 |isbn=0-86793-035-7 }}</ref>

;1972
:中國的研究成功以[[富來頓|富來頓]] （一種抗生素）治療消化性潰瘍。<ref name="XSL-hp">{{cite book |last=Xiao |chapter=How we discovered in China in 1972 that antibiotics cure peptic ulcer |editor=Barry J. Marshall |title=Helicobacter pioneers: firsthand accounts from the scientists who discovered helicobacters, 1892–1982 |publisher=Blackwell |location=Oxford |year=2002 |pages=165–202 |isbn=0-86793-035-7 |first=Shu Dong  }}</ref>

;1974
:莫洛索夫（Morozov）觀察到幽門螺桿菌，但他沒有將此發現與消化性潰瘍做連結。<ref name="IM-hp" />
:派翠克（Patrick）等人發表了一份傑出的消化性潰瘍研究，但內容完全沒有提到細菌。<ref name="HWS-hp" /><ref>{{cite journal |last=Patrick |first=W.J.A. |author2=D. Denham |author3=A.P.M. Forrest|year=1974 |title=Mucous change in the human duodenum: A light and electron microscopic study and correlation with disease and gastric acid secretion |journal=Gut |volume=15 |issue=10|pages=767–76| pmid = 4434919 |doi=10.1136/gut.15.10.767 |pmc=1412991}}</ref>

[[Image:Pseudomonas_aeruginosa_01.jpg|thumb]]（''Pseudomonas aeruginosa''），一種假單胞菌]]
;1975
:史提爾（Steer）和柯林-瓊斯（Colin-Jones）發表了他們研究幽門螺桿菌與消化性潰瘍間關係的成果，認為之前發現的細菌其實是[[假單胞菌屬|假單胞菌]]（''Pseudomonas''）污染，且此菌和消化性潰瘍沒有關係。<ref>{{cite journal |last=Steer |first=H.W. |author2=D.G. Colin-Jones  |year=1975 |title=Mucosal changes in gastric ulceration and their response to carbenoxolone sodium |journal=Gut |volume=16 |issue=8|pages=590–7| pmid = 810394 |doi=10.1136/gut.16.8.590 |pmc=1411007}}</ref>

;1978
:美國腸胃學協會在[[拉斯維加斯|拉斯維加斯]]的一場會議上，數份研究指出使用[[H2受體阻抗劑|H<sub>2</sub>受體阻抗劑]]控制胃酸對消化性潰瘍的治療效果很差。<ref name="PHM-hp">{{cite book |author=Peterson, Walter L |chapter=The Dallas experience with acute ''Helicobacter pylori'' infection |editor=Barry J. Marshall |title=Helicobacter pioneers: firsthand accounts from the scientists who discovered helicobacters, 1892–1982 |publisher=Blackwell |location=Oxford |year=2002 |pages=143–50 |isbn=0-86793-035-7 }}</ref>

;1979
:拉姆塞（Ramsey）發表的研究顯示鉍能幫助治癒消化性潰瘍，鉍是一種抗菌物質，雖然拉姆塞並沒有認可這種說法。<ref>{{cite journal |last=Ramsey |first=E.J. |year=1979 |title=Epidemic gastritis with hypochlorhydria |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_gastroenterology_1979-06_76_6/page/1449 |journal=Gastroenterology |volume=76|issue=6 |pages=1449–57 | pmid = 437444 |name-list-format=vanc|author2=K.V. Carey |author3=W.L. Peterson |display-authors=2 |last4=Jackson |first4=JJ |last5=Murphy |first5=FK |last6=Read |first6=NW |last7=Taylor |first7=KB |last8=Trier |first8=JS |last9=Fordtran |first9=JS}}</ref>
:華倫（J. Robin Warren）首先在胃檢體的切片中發現了幽門螺桿菌。<ref name="JRW-hp">{{cite book |author=Warren, J. Robin |chapter=The discovery of ''Helicobacter pylori'' in Perth, Western Australia |editor=Barry J. Marshall |title=Helicobacter pioneers: firsthand accounts from the scientists who discovered helicobacters, 1892–1982 |publisher=Blackwell |location=Oxford |year=2002 |pages=151–64 |isbn=0-86793-035-7 }}</ref>
:馮（Fung）、帕帕季米特里烏（Papadimitriou）和馬茲（Matz）觀察到幽門螺桿菌。<ref>{{cite journal |last=Fung |first=W.P. |author2=J.M Papadimitriou |author3=L.R. Matz |year=1979 |title=Endoscopic, histological and ultrastructural correlations in chronic gastritis |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_american-journal-of-gastroenterology_1979-03_71_3/page/n32 |journal=American Journal of Gastroenterology |volume=71|issue = 3 |pages=269–79| pmid = 443229 }}</ref>

;1981
:施堯在胃內觀察到彎曲的細菌，但認為它們只是通過胃部的過客，而沒有進行培養。<ref name="XSL-hp" />
:7月：巴里·馬歇爾進入{{le|皇家佩思醫院|Royal Perth Hospital}}腸胃學科，遇到了羅賓·沃倫。<ref name="BM-hp">{{cite book |author=Marshall, Barry |chapter=The discovery that ''Helicobacter pylori'', a spiral bacterium, caused peptic ulcer disease |editor=Barry J. Marshall |title=Helicobacter pioneers: firsthand accounts from the scientists who discovered helicobacters, 1892–1982 |publisher=Blackwell |location=Oxford |year=2002 |pages=165–202 |isbn=0-86793-035-7 }}</ref>
:10月：馬歇爾和沃倫成功用抗生素治癒了他們的第一個消化性潰瘍病患。<ref name="BM-hp" />

[[Image:Cimetidine_structure.svg|thumb]]
;1983
:1月：兩份分別由沃倫和馬歇爾署名的研究快訊送至學術期刊《[[刺胳針_(雜誌)|刺胳針]]》，當中描述了他們的研究成果。<ref name="BM-hp" />
:2月：澳洲腸胃學會拒絕馬歇爾在年度會議上發表研究，並將他送來的論文摘要評為所有投稿中最差的10%。但同樣的稿件為布魯塞爾曲狀桿菌工作坊所接受，並准予他在論壇中發表成果。<ref name="BM-hp" />
:4月：馬歇爾和伊恩·希斯洛普（Ian Hislop）開始比較鉍和西咪替丁（Cimetidine）對消化性潰瘍的療效，但最後因為無法得到有效的結論，他們放棄了這項研究。<ref name="BM-hp" />
:6月：沃倫和馬歇爾的研究快訊出現在《刺胳針》上。<ref name="WM-l">{{cite journal |last=Warren |first=J.R. |author2=Barry Marshall  |year=1983 |title=Unidentified curved bacilli on gastric epithelium in active chronic gastritis |journal=Lancet |volume= 1| issue = 8336 |pages=1273–5| pmid = 6134060 | doi = 10.1016/S0140-6736(83)92719-8}}</ref>
:9月：澳洲以外的消化性潰瘍病人身上也觀察到了幽門螺桿菌。<ref name="BM-hp" />
:沃倫和馬歇爾的研究快訊出現在《刺胳針》後，全世界的研究團隊都開始分離幽門螺桿菌。<ref name="BM-hp" />

;1984
:馬歇爾和沃倫的研究報告獲得澳洲腸胃學會接受並准予發表。<ref name="BM-hp" />
:馬歇爾和古德溫（Goodwin）嘗試用幽門螺桿菌感染豬，但沒有造成豬的消化性潰瘍，以失敗收場。<ref name="BM-hp" />
:5月：馬歇爾和沃倫的研究報告獲《刺胳針》接受，並於隔月刊出，但遭來許多批評。<ref name="BM-hp" />
:麥納提（McNulty）和華生（Watson）成功重現馬歇爾和沃倫的結果。<ref>{{cite journal |last=McNulty |first=C.A. |author2=D.M. Watson  |year=1984 |title=Spiral bacteria of the gastric antrum |journal=The Lancet |volume = 1 | issue = 8385 |pages=1068–9 | pmid = 6143990 |doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(84)91469-7}}</ref>
:6月12日：馬歇爾有意地吃下幽門螺桿菌並造成自己生病，他隨後服用抗生素，並成功解除症狀。<ref name="BM-hp" />
:澳洲{{le|國家健康暨醫藥研究委員會|National Health and Medical Research Council}}全額資助馬歇爾研究幽門螺桿菌。<ref name="BM-hp" />
:中國刊出一篇研究，講述抗菌物質能有效治療消化性潰瘍。<ref name="XSL-hp" />
:7月31日：《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》的醫學專欄作家阿特曼醫師（Dr. Lawrence K. Altman）發表一篇文章，說明幽門螺桿菌和消化性潰瘍之間可能的關聯性。<ref name="altman19840731">{{cite news | url=http://www.nytimes.com/1984/07/31/science/new-bacterium-linked-to-painful-stomach-ills.html?pagewanted=all | title=NEW BACTERIUM LINKED TO PAINFUL STOMACH ILLS | accessdate=March 12, 2011 | author=Altman, Lawrence K. | date=1984-07-31 | publisher=The New York Times | archive-date=2016-03-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303223853/http://www.nytimes.com/1984/07/31/science/new-bacterium-linked-to-painful-stomach-ills.html?pagewanted=all | dead-url=no }}</ref> 他在2002年說道：「我從來沒看過醫學社群對一個故事的發展採取如此防衛且挑剔的態度」，而他從1969年加入新聞業以來已經30多年。<ref name="humphrey20020927">{{cite news | url=http://www.mc.vanderbilt.edu/reporter/index.html?ID=2278 | title=Award-winning journalist informs doctors, world | accessdate=March 12, 2011 | author=Humphrey, Nancy | date=2002-09-27 | publisher=The Reporter, Vanderbilt University Medical Center's Weekly Newspaper | archive-date=2018-12-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181230181058/https://www.mc.vanderbilt.edu/reporter/index.html?ID=2278 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

;1985
:馬歇爾發表了他刻意感染自己的研究成果。<ref name="BM-hp" />

;1987
:德拉姆（Drumm）與其同事將針對兒童的研究報告發表在《[[新英格蘭醫學雜誌|新英格蘭醫學雜誌]]》上，指出幽門螺桿菌只和原發性胃炎、無法解釋的胃炎、及原發性十二指腸潰瘍有關，其它如[[克隆氏症|克隆氏症]]或重大疾病所造成的次級胃炎則和細菌無關。由於兒童的胃炎和十二指腸潰瘍很少見，因此這份研究有足夠的說服力說明幽門螺桿菌是胃炎的致病原，而非僅是在發炎或潰瘍的黏膜上伺機繁殖，這也就證明沃倫和馬歇爾是正確的。這是全球首屈一指的學術期刊《新英格蘭醫學雜誌》第一次刊登和幽門螺桿菌相關的研究。<ref>{{cite journal | author = Drumm B |display-authors=etal | year = 1987 | title = Association of Campylobacter pylori on the gastric mucosa with antral gastritis in children | url = | journal = New England Journal of Medicine | volume = 316 | issue = | pages = 1557–1661 | doi=10.1056/nejm198706183162501}}</ref> 
:莫利斯（Morris）刻意服下幽門螺桿菌後生病了，但和馬歇爾不同的是，抗生素無法完全治癒他的疾病，感染持續了三年之久。<ref>{{cite journal |last=Morris |first=A. |author2=G. Nicholson  |year=1987 |title=Ingestion of Campylobacter pyloridis causes gastritis and raised fasting gastric pH |journal=American Journal of Gastroenterology | volume = 82 | issue = 3|pages=192–9| pmid = 3826027 }}</ref>
:都柏林的一項大規模研究指出消除幽門螺桿菌能大幅降低潰瘍復發的機率。<ref>{{cite journal |last=Coghlan |first=J.G. |year=1987 |title=Campylobacter pylori and recurrence of duodenal ulcers—a 12-month follow-up study |journal=The Lancet |volume = 2 | issue = 8568|pages=109–11| pmid = 2890019 |doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(02)93231-9 |name-list-format=vanc|author2=H. Humphrise |author3=C. Dooley |display-authors=2 |last4=McKenna |first4=D |last5=Dooley |first5=C |last6=Sweeney |first6=E |last7=Keane |first7=C |last8=O'Morain |first8=C }}</ref>

;1990
:羅斯（Rauws）和提特蓋特（Tytgat）以鉍和兩種抗生素組成的三聯療法消除幽門螺桿菌，成功治癒十二指腸潰瘍。<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Rauws E, Tytgat G | title = Cure of duodenal ulcer associated with eradication of Helicobacter pylori | journal = Lancet | volume = 335 | issue = 8700 | pages = 1233–5 | year = 1990 | pmid = 1971318 | doi = 10.1016/0140-6736(90)91301-P}}</ref> 現代的三聯療法則改用[[氫離子幫浦阻斷劑|氫離子幫浦阻斷劑]]和兩種抗生素，並很快成為了治療首選；使用氫離子幫浦阻斷劑的用意在於抑制胃液的酸度，使胃內不再適合幽門螺桿菌生長。<ref name=Maas />。
:世界腸胃學會議建議消除幽門螺桿菌以治療十二指腸潰瘍。<ref name=":1">{{cite journal |last=Rauws |first=E.A.J. |author2=G.N.J. Tytgat  |year=1990 |title=Cure of duodenal ulcer associated with eradication of Helicobacter pylori |journal=The Lancet |volume = 335 | issue = 8700|pages=1233–5| pmid = 1971318 |doi=10.1016/0140-6736(90)91301-P }}</ref>
:首次有報告指出幽門螺桿菌對[[甲硝唑|甲硝唑]]產生抗藥性<ref>{{cite journal | author = Becx M| title = Metronidazole-resistant Helicobacter pylori | journal = Lancet | volume = 335 | issue = 8688 | pages = 539–40 | year = 1990 | pmid = 1968548| doi = 10.1016/0140-6736(90)90772-W |name-list-format=vanc| author2 = Janssen A | display-authors = 2 | last3 = Clasener | first3 = H.A.L. | last4 = De Koning | first4 = R.W.}}</ref>。此次發現的抗藥性導致未來發展出各式使用抗生素和氫離子幫浦阻斷劑的療法<ref name=Maas>{{cite journal | author = Malfertheiner P| title = Current concepts in the management of Helicobacter pylori infection—the Maastricht 2-2000 Consensus Report | journal = Aliment Pharmacol Ther | volume = 16 | issue = 2 | pages = 167–80 | year = 2002 | pmid = 11860399| doi = 10.1046/j.1365-2036.2002.01169.x |name-list-format=vanc| author2 = Mégraud F | author3 = O'Morain C | display-authors = 3 | last4 = Hungin | first4 = A. P. S. | last5 = Jones | first5 = R. | last6 = Axon | first6 = A. | last7 = Graham | first7 = D. Y. | last8 = Tytgat | first8 = G. | author9 = European Helicobacter Pylori Study Group (EHPSG)}}</ref>。

;1992
:福田善弘等人證明[[恆河猴|恆河猴]]食入幽門螺桿菌後會造成胃炎。<ref name="FSSM-hp" />
:科瓦奇（Covacci）成功定序出CagA基因， 該基因[[遗传密码|編碼]]的[[細胞毒性|細胞毒素]]和幽門螺桿菌造成的十二指腸潰瘍有密切關係。這是科學家第一次以[[分子生物学|分子生物學]]技術確認幽門螺桿菌的{{le|致病因子|virulence factor}}。<ref>{{cite journal | author = Covacci A| title = Molecular characterization of the 128-kDa immunodominant antigen of Helicobacter pylori associated with cytotoxicity and duodenal ulcer | journal = Proc Natl Acad Sci USA | volume = 90 | issue = 12 | pages = 5791–5 | year = 1993 | pmid = 8516329| doi = 10.1073/pnas.90.12.5791 | pmc = 46808 |name-list-format=vanc| author2 = Censini S | author3 = Bugnoli M | display-authors = 3 | last4 = Petracca | first4 = R | last5 = Burroni | first5 = D | last6 = MacChia | first6 = G | last7 = Massone | first7 = A | last8 = Papini | first8 = E | last9 = Xiang | first9 = Z}}</ref>

[[Image:Linitis_plastica.jpg|thumb]]
;1994
:藤岡利生等人得到和福田善弘相似的結果。<ref name="FSSM-hp" />
:抗酸藥專利過期，相關利益人士失去了拒絕使用抗生素治療幽門螺桿菌的財務動機。<ref name="BM-hp" />
:美國[[國立衛生研究院_(美國)|國立衛生研究院]]舉辦的會議顯示美國科學家已普遍接受幽門螺桿菌是造成消化性潰瘍的原因。<ref name="BM-hp" />
:[[世界衛生組織|世界衛生組織]][[國際癌症研究機構|國際癌症研究機構]]公告幽門螺桿菌為第一類[[致癌物|致癌物]]。<ref name=":2">{{cite web|title=List of Agents Classified by the IARC Monographs |author=WHO International Agency for Research on Cancer |url=http://monographs.iarc.fr/ENG/Classification/List_of_Classifications.pdf |accessdate=2016-09-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160905203045/http://monographs.iarc.fr/ENG/Classification/List_of_Classifications.pdf |archivedate=2016-09-05 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>
:帕爾森內特（Parsonnet）等人闡述了幽門螺桿菌和腸胃道[[淋巴癌|淋巴癌]]之間的關聯，這些{{le|黏膜相關淋巴組織淋巴瘤|MALT lymphoma|惡性}}潰瘍也能以消滅幽門螺桿菌的方式治療。<ref>{{cite journal | author = Parsonnet J | title = Helicobacter pylori infection and gastric lymphoma | journal = New England Journal of Medicine | volume = 330 | issue = 18 | pages = 1267–71 | year = 1994 | pmid = 8145781 | doi = 10.1056/NEJM199405053301803 |name-list-format=vanc| author2 = Hansen S | author3 = Rodriguez L | display-authors = 3 | last4 = Gelb | first4 = Arnold B. | last5 = Warnke | first5 = Roger A. | last6 = Jellum | first6 = Egil | last7 = Orentreich | first7 = Norman | last8 = Vogelman | first8 = Joseph H. | last9 = Friedman | first9 = Gary D.}}</ref>

;1997
